Path: **`salons/{salonId}/bookings/{bookingId}`** — model: `lib/features/bookings/data/models/booking.dart`.

Bookings are **only** under a salon subcollection (**not** `bookings/{bookingId}` at root).

## Fields

id: string
salonId: string (must match path)
barberId: string (`employees/{employeeId}` doc id)
barberName: string (optional, denormalized)
customerId: string (`users/{uid}`)
customerName: string (optional, denormalized)
serviceId: string (optional)
serviceName: string (optional, denormalized)
startAt: timestamp
endAt: timestamp
status: string — `BookingStatuses`: scheduled | confirmed | completed | cancelled | no_show
notes: string (optional)
reportYear: number
reportMonth: number
reportPeriodKey: string (YYYY-MM)
createdAt: timestamp
updatedAt: timestamp

## Implemented vs Planned

**Implemented:** Path and fields match `Booking` / `BookingRepository`.

**Planned:** e.g. `price` / deposit on the booking document if product adds payments per booking.
